                              </mrow>
                            </annotation-xml>
                          </semantics>
                        </math> When Bohr calculated his theoretical value for the Rydberg constant,
                        <math display="inline">
                          <semantics>
                            <mrow>
                              <mrow>
                                <msub>
                                  <mi>R</mi>
                                  <mi>∞</mi>
                                </msub>
