                          <em data-effect="italics">n</em> = 5 to the
                          <em data-effect="italics">n</em> = 3 level in a He
                          <sup>+</sup> ion (
                          <em data-effect="italics">Z</em> = 2 for He
                          <sup>+</sup>)?
